Package: CDSMutSig
Type: Package
Title: Mapping Coding Sequences between DNA Mutational signatures and Amino Acid Changes
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Joseph Ng, Franca Fraternali
Maintainer: Joseph Ng <joseph.chifung.ng@gmail.com>
Description: A set of functions which use Ensembl and Bioconductor genome objects to map between given protein sequences to corresponding coding DNA sequences, extract single-amino acid variants (SNVs) and corresponding nucleotide substitutions.
    Map mutational signatures for all possible substitutions.
License: GPL
Encoding: UTF-8
